  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >video streaming OK!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/fa9c5fdf50708c4c869f26ef941286b2.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/fa9c5fdf50708c4c869f26ef941286b2.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a <strong>ping pong ball</strong> and a <strong>ping pong racket</strong> to move up and reach the goal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are four stages: <strong>Easy</strong> stage, <strong>Normal</strong> stage, <strong>Hard</strong> stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 stages. Challenge yourself to go higher!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The way to play is to move the ping-pong racket with the mouse, which requires simple reflexes. While the simple controls allow you to enjoy the dynamic destruction of blocks, there are various gimmicks and obstacles waiting for you along the way, so it is not easy to advance.The game is a thrilling experience that requires players to use their reflexes to conquer the stages and break through the gimmicks that stand in their way one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/b62b82ef6bc8d292be940e4dcbd56ee0.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/b62b82ef6bc8d292be940e4dcbd56ee0.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/ffeaf9f18f83116c0b78934cbbcaf82f.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/ffeaf9f18f83116c0b78934cbbcaf82f.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you get tired of ping pong balls, try hitting the TV.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >video streaming OK!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/fa9c5fdf50708c4c869f26ef941286b2.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/fa9c5fdf50708c4c869f26ef941286b2.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a <strong>ping pong ball</strong> and a <strong>ping pong racket</strong> to move up and reach the goal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are four stages: <strong>Easy</strong> stage, <strong>Normal</strong> stage, <strong>Hard</strong> stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 stages. Challenge yourself to go higher!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The way to play is to move the ping-pong racket with the mouse, which requires simple reflexes. While the simple controls allow you to enjoy the dynamic destruction of blocks, there are various gimmicks and obstacles waiting for you along the way, so it is not easy to advance.The game is a thrilling experience that requires players to use their reflexes to conquer the stages and break through the gimmicks that stand in their way one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/b62b82ef6bc8d292be940e4dcbd56ee0.avif?t=1760811215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras_big/b62b82ef6bc8d292be940e4dcbd56ee0.avif?t=1760811215 width=800 height=600 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3117950/extras/ffeaf9f18f83116c0b78934cbbcaf82f.avif?t=1760811215\"